Package: eavsr
Title: Tidy Access to the Election Administration and Voting Survey
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cameron", "Wimpy", , "cwimpy@astate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2049-5229"))
Description: A tidy interface to the U.S. Election Assistance Commission's
    Election Administration and Voting Survey (EAVS). Downloads and caches
    public-release files, harmonizes variable names across survey cycles,
    exposes the codebook as a tibble, and provides helpers for joining EAVS
    data to county-level rurality classifications. Not affiliated with or
    endorsed by the U.S. Election Assistance Commission.
